WEBVTT

01:52.210 --> 01:57.550
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.570 --> 02:01.990
[Episode 14]

02:02.860 --> 02:03.900
This reform plan

02:04.560 --> 02:05.560
reflects the importance

02:05.560 --> 02:07.890
of the national selection exam
in a comprehensive way.

02:07.890 --> 02:08.820
It not only offers

02:08.820 --> 02:10.940
commoners a chance
to change their fate,

02:10.940 --> 02:12.120
but also injects fresh talent

02:12.120 --> 02:14.450
into many official posts
across the Nine Cities.

02:14.450 --> 02:16.120
Both in public and private interests,

02:16.120 --> 02:17.410
it is an excellent way

02:17.430 --> 02:19.190
to rejuvenate the Nine Cities.

02:20.040 --> 02:20.990
In time,

02:21.370 --> 02:23.400
men and women of ambition
from all over the Nine Cities

02:23.400 --> 02:24.620
will gather in Ling'an,

02:24.620 --> 02:26.350
vying to serve the Nine Cities.

02:27.079 --> 02:29.030
The happiness and well-being
of the people within the cities,

02:29.030 --> 02:30.870
and the long-lasting prosperity
of the Nine Cities,

02:30.870 --> 02:33.020
will be ensured from this day forward.

02:35.690 --> 02:36.550
How about that—

02:37.190 --> 02:39.150
what do you all think,
my esteemed ministers?

02:39.150 --> 02:41.010
Is there anything further to add?

02:42.300 --> 02:44.460
This draft is comprehensive
and covers all aspects.

02:44.460 --> 02:46.490
It even provides a detailed analysis

02:46.490 --> 02:48.480
of the educational conditions
in each city,

02:48.480 --> 02:50.630
and carefully compiles
and investigates the identities

02:50.630 --> 02:53.110
of students of examination age.

02:55.470 --> 02:57.920
I can hardly find a single flaw in it.

02:58.520 --> 03:01.920
Your Excellency, it seems you have
truly gone to great lengths

03:01.920 --> 03:04.120
and have been well prepared in advance.

03:04.460 --> 03:05.060
Oh,

03:06.240 --> 03:07.370
in addition to this,

03:07.950 --> 03:08.410
there is

03:09.080 --> 03:10.240
also a review of the service records

03:10.240 --> 03:12.630
of officials from various departments
across the Nine Cities.

03:12.630 --> 03:14.260
It is clearly shown here
that the officials

03:14.260 --> 03:16.079
of the Granary Affairs Division
of the Commerce Bureau—

03:16.079 --> 03:17.230
though charged with grain storage

03:17.230 --> 03:18.630
and granary management—

03:19.250 --> 03:20.910
were born into noble families

03:21.120 --> 03:23.520
and had never experienced
the hardships of agricultural labor.

03:23.520 --> 03:24.120
Their handling of policies

03:24.120 --> 03:26.630
such as the Green Sprouts law,
labor-commutation,

03:26.630 --> 03:27.870
and farmland irrigation regulations

03:27.870 --> 03:29.600
contains many improprieties,

03:29.640 --> 03:31.910
which has led
to the current growing disorder

03:31.910 --> 03:33.910
in the management
of official farmland estates.

03:33.910 --> 03:34.820
It seems that

03:35.540 --> 03:36.500
over the years,

03:36.710 --> 03:37.710
candidates selected
through the selection exam

03:37.710 --> 03:40.150
have largely come
from the Nine Noble Families.

03:40.150 --> 03:40.900
As a result,

03:41.030 --> 03:44.490
the composition of officials
has become overly homogeneous.

03:44.510 --> 03:45.020
Right.

03:45.329 --> 03:47.130
I had originally assumed Your Excellency

03:47.130 --> 03:49.280
was only skilled
in feasting and leisure,

03:49.280 --> 03:50.340
but I did not expect

03:50.630 --> 03:52.230
your mind to be so meticulous

03:52.760 --> 03:54.160
and your vision so broad—

03:54.670 --> 03:58.450
you are in fact deeply concerned
with the affairs of the Nine Cities.

03:58.450 --> 04:00.850
As the saying goes, one cannot
measure the sea with a bucket;

04:00.850 --> 04:01.970
nor can one

04:02.080 --> 04:03.740
underestimate the governor.

04:04.150 --> 04:05.140
Indeed.

04:05.390 --> 04:07.140
With this draft,

04:07.400 --> 04:10.190
and the full support
of all ministers,

04:11.030 --> 04:13.560
we should be able to stand
against Lord Zheng.

04:16.140 --> 04:16.860
However,

04:17.310 --> 04:18.829
we, the Three Elders,

04:19.680 --> 04:21.430
may end up breaking apart.

04:23.480 --> 04:24.600
In truth, reform

04:25.050 --> 04:27.550
has always been
my long-cherished aspiration.

04:27.550 --> 04:29.140
For the sake of the people
of the Nine Cities,

04:29.140 --> 04:30.670
this reform is imperative.

04:31.920 --> 04:34.310
Therefore,
at tomorrow's morning assembly,

04:34.310 --> 04:36.710
I will promulgate this draft
to the public.

04:37.510 --> 04:39.770
If there are any objections at that time,

04:39.840 --> 04:41.300
I hope all of you ministers

04:41.520 --> 04:42.620
will argue our case

04:42.800 --> 04:43.830
with reason.

04:46.810 --> 04:48.900
We shall do our utmost.

05:00.520 --> 05:02.690
[Juyun Gate]

05:03.310 --> 05:05.870
Today, although some of you
have already expressed your positions,

05:05.870 --> 05:06.560
I understand

05:06.560 --> 05:08.220
your concerns and confusion.

05:08.970 --> 05:11.370
Please go back
and give it further thought.

05:12.480 --> 05:13.940
The meeting is adjourned.

05:15.180 --> 05:16.560
I really didn't expect things

05:16.560 --> 05:18.090
to turn out like this today.

05:18.390 --> 05:20.550
Lord Zheng does make quite a lot of sense.

05:20.550 --> 05:21.750
Lord Lyu also...

05:23.100 --> 05:23.900
Lord Zheng.

05:23.920 --> 05:24.780
Lord Zheng.

05:27.390 --> 05:28.040
Lord...

05:28.330 --> 05:29.360
Lord Zhao.

05:34.290 --> 05:36.290
This is going to be serious trouble.

05:49.550 --> 05:50.790
Zhao,

05:52.090 --> 05:53.370
I always thought

05:54.190 --> 05:56.320
the bond between us, the Three Elders,

05:56.430 --> 05:58.100
was unbreakable.

05:58.490 --> 06:00.270
Indeed, it is.

06:01.930 --> 06:04.670
So how did things come to this—
how did we end up breaking our word?

06:04.670 --> 06:05.650
Who?

06:06.080 --> 06:07.540
I'm talking about someone

06:08.200 --> 06:09.750
who supported the governor's

06:09.750 --> 06:11.780
selection exam reform draft—

06:13.720 --> 06:15.810
trifling with me like this,

06:16.200 --> 06:19.290
thinking nothing of me!

06:19.320 --> 06:20.520
Zheng,

06:21.670 --> 06:25.330
how could I possibly
be trifling with you, Lord Zheng Yuan?

06:25.360 --> 06:26.750
That's too harsh.

06:26.750 --> 06:28.740
Stop putting on an act.

06:30.640 --> 06:32.360
Let it be that I, Zheng,

06:32.790 --> 06:34.090
misjudged you—

06:35.030 --> 06:36.630
and my sincerity was wasted.

06:38.040 --> 06:39.040
If the foundation

06:39.390 --> 06:41.150
of the Nine Cities

06:41.170 --> 06:43.240
is ruined in my hands,

06:43.510 --> 06:46.890
how am I supposed to face
the trust of the late governor?

06:48.810 --> 06:51.159
Zheng, calm down first

06:51.990 --> 06:53.310
and listen to me.

06:53.390 --> 06:55.159
The governor's temperament

06:55.159 --> 06:56.560
is very much like the late governor—

06:56.560 --> 07:00.560
once he sets his mind on something,
he will not rest until he achieves it.

07:01.750 --> 07:03.540
As ministers,

07:03.660 --> 07:06.220
how could we possibly oppose the governor?

07:06.840 --> 07:07.750
Exactly.

07:09.310 --> 07:10.000
Zheng,

07:10.600 --> 07:13.070
the selection exam has been in place
for so many years.

07:13.070 --> 07:14.070
A reform wouldn't

07:14.650 --> 07:16.410
necessarily be a bad thing.

07:18.270 --> 07:19.360
Zheng,

07:20.160 --> 07:21.600
on this matter,

07:22.500 --> 07:24.410
I actually stand on your side.

07:25.550 --> 07:27.180
But what the governor is doing

07:27.180 --> 07:28.810
hasn't crossed a point

07:29.520 --> 07:30.460
of no return yet,

07:31.720 --> 07:34.080
so there's no need
to make things difficult for him.

07:34.080 --> 07:35.110
Just agree to it.

07:35.800 --> 07:37.159
Didn't the governor say it?

07:37.159 --> 07:39.360
The draft will be implemented for 1 year

07:39.480 --> 07:42.280
without relying
on the support of noble families.

07:42.480 --> 07:44.409
If external assistance is needed,

07:44.440 --> 07:45.530
that would prove

07:45.550 --> 07:46.909
the commoner path to office

07:46.909 --> 07:48.710
is not viable.

07:48.730 --> 07:49.650
After 1 year,

07:49.680 --> 07:53.350
wouldn't we simply abolish
the national selection exam?

07:55.600 --> 07:57.390
You two...

07:58.750 --> 08:00.950
Fine. Fine. Fine.

08:07.390 --> 08:09.940
I've worked with you both for many years—

08:12.240 --> 08:14.360
I treated you as friends.

08:14.600 --> 08:16.040
And yet, you...

08:19.510 --> 08:20.720
If even

08:20.720 --> 08:22.450
women are to be included

08:22.630 --> 08:24.240
in the selection exam,

08:24.240 --> 08:27.190
the nature of the system
will change.

08:28.000 --> 08:30.630
The civil and military officials
would not agree to it.

08:30.630 --> 08:32.080
A-A-And furthermore...

08:33.270 --> 08:34.750
Forget it.

08:36.919 --> 08:38.159
From this point on,

08:38.909 --> 08:40.039
you two

08:40.510 --> 08:42.350
take your path,

08:42.789 --> 08:45.030
and I'll take mine.

08:45.770 --> 08:46.720
With that,

08:47.280 --> 08:48.350
I take my leave.

08:49.140 --> 08:51.020
W-Wait, Zheng! Zheng!

08:51.040 --> 08:52.040
Zheng.

08:53.670 --> 08:54.490
Zheng,

08:55.430 --> 08:57.180
please, let's talk this through.

08:57.180 --> 08:57.960
You...

08:58.440 --> 08:58.940
You...

09:03.150 --> 09:05.080
Didn't we agree the three of us

09:05.100 --> 09:07.790
would protect the foundation
of the Nine Cities together?

09:07.790 --> 09:09.120
Now see what happens...

09:12.790 --> 09:15.780
I am protecting the foundation
of the Nine Cities—

09:16.850 --> 09:18.110
just in a slightly different way

09:18.110 --> 09:19.150
from Zheng,

09:19.790 --> 09:21.790
that's all.

09:23.360 --> 09:24.960
You call that "slightly different"?

09:24.960 --> 09:26.790
That's going in completely
opposite directions.

09:26.790 --> 09:27.650
They're practically

09:27.650 --> 09:29.580
as incompatible as fire and water.

09:30.170 --> 09:31.100
Look—

09:31.840 --> 09:32.360
no,

09:32.360 --> 09:33.470
Lyu,

09:35.030 --> 09:35.810
tell me,

09:36.320 --> 09:37.200
what

09:37.550 --> 09:39.200
should we do next?

09:44.360 --> 09:45.660
What else can we do?

09:46.510 --> 09:48.040
We'll just wait until Zheng

09:48.360 --> 09:49.600
cools down,

09:50.890 --> 09:52.150
and deal with it later.

10:00.480 --> 10:01.220
Fan Yun,

10:01.870 --> 10:03.960
Fan Yun, I appoint you
as the head of all officials.

10:03.960 --> 10:05.220
From this day forward,

10:05.360 --> 10:07.260
you shall be second only to me—

10:07.550 --> 10:08.750
and above all others.

10:09.270 --> 10:11.150
Whether commoners or officials,

10:11.600 --> 10:13.200
all shall obey your command.

10:13.290 --> 10:17.130
Congratulations, Fan Yun. Congratulations!

10:34.130 --> 10:35.040
Zheng Yuan!

10:35.070 --> 10:36.280
Late governor.

10:40.000 --> 10:43.260
The national selection exam
is throwing the Nine Cities into chaos—

10:43.260 --> 10:44.930
what face do you still have

10:44.960 --> 10:46.250
to remain in office?

10:48.980 --> 10:50.050
Master,

10:50.080 --> 10:51.130
are you all right?

11:00.410 --> 11:01.560
Prepare the sedan immediately.

11:01.560 --> 11:02.960
I need to enter the manor.

11:08.320 --> 11:09.720
Your condition isn't suitable

11:09.720 --> 11:11.480
for entering the manor right now.

11:11.480 --> 11:12.610
If there's anything,

11:12.610 --> 11:14.610
just let me go on your behalf.

11:15.480 --> 11:16.670
Very well.

11:20.240 --> 11:21.610
Make sure this letter

11:22.150 --> 11:24.480
is delivered personally to the governor.

11:25.200 --> 11:25.790
Go.

11:25.790 --> 11:26.750
Yes, Master.

11:28.150 --> 11:28.900
Hold on.

11:32.630 --> 11:33.700
If you

11:34.270 --> 11:36.020
run into Lord Lyu,

11:38.510 --> 11:39.640
keep your distance.

11:54.230 --> 11:55.230
Zheng Yi!

11:58.380 --> 11:59.240
Zheng Yi.

12:01.960 --> 12:04.320
The more I think about it,
the angrier I get.

12:04.320 --> 12:05.270
I never expected that,

12:05.270 --> 12:06.510
compared to commoners,

12:06.510 --> 12:08.890
they would be even more afraid
of women entering officialdom.

12:08.890 --> 12:09.890
Your Excellency,

12:10.130 --> 12:11.260
please have some tea

12:12.790 --> 12:13.850
to calm your anger.

12:16.470 --> 12:20.040
If it weren't for Your Excellency's
strategic maneuvering

12:20.840 --> 12:23.320
and timely proposal for reconsideration,

12:23.320 --> 12:25.320
this reform of the selection exam

12:25.320 --> 12:27.550
might have come to nothing
at the last moment.

12:27.550 --> 12:28.600
If you ask me,

12:29.720 --> 12:32.180
Lord Zheng is indeed
somewhat overbearing,

12:33.030 --> 12:36.160
but he has also been doing
his utmost for the Nine Cities.

12:37.390 --> 12:38.320
Lord Lyu,

12:39.000 --> 12:41.320
you really should try
to persuade Lord Zheng.

12:41.320 --> 12:43.650
After all, whether this succeeds or fails

12:43.870 --> 12:45.120
will still depend

12:45.120 --> 12:47.580
on whether we can
gain Lord Zheng's support.

12:56.840 --> 12:58.240
I will

12:58.240 --> 13:00.570
certainly do my utmost, Your Excellency.

13:04.360 --> 13:06.080
Come on, try some.

13:10.750 --> 13:11.440
These are

13:11.440 --> 13:13.500
sesame balls I made with my own hands.

13:13.870 --> 13:14.950
I just wanted

13:15.270 --> 13:16.670
to properly thank you all

13:17.480 --> 13:19.240
for taking care

13:19.240 --> 13:20.500
of me during this time.

13:21.200 --> 13:22.060
I didn't expect

13:22.150 --> 13:23.650
Fan Xiu to have such cooking skills.

13:23.650 --> 13:25.320
Delicious, delicious.

13:25.490 --> 13:27.300
Nice. Nice. Nice.

13:28.120 --> 13:28.880
But...

13:29.390 --> 13:30.990
you're leaving, aren't you?

13:31.970 --> 13:32.800
Honestly,

13:32.820 --> 13:34.480
you've been here so many days—

13:34.640 --> 13:36.150
we're quite reluctant to see you go.

13:36.150 --> 13:37.130
Yes, yes.

13:37.360 --> 13:39.760
There's still some time
before the selection exam.

13:39.760 --> 13:41.690
Why are you in such a hurry to leave?

13:42.390 --> 13:44.190
I want to spend the remaining days

13:44.190 --> 13:45.570
studying hard

13:46.110 --> 13:47.480
and preparing for the selection exam.

13:47.480 --> 13:48.870
Fan Xiu, once you
pass the selection exam,

13:48.870 --> 13:50.530
you must come to our Commerce Bureau.

13:50.530 --> 13:52.270
We'll all be thinking of you.

13:52.290 --> 13:53.010
Yes, yes,

13:53.040 --> 13:54.640
we'll all be thinking of you.

13:55.630 --> 13:56.830
After Fan Xiu leaves,

13:56.870 --> 13:57.670
Lord Jiang

13:58.040 --> 14:00.300
will definitely increase our workload—

14:01.330 --> 14:02.610
our good days

14:03.150 --> 14:04.480
are over.

14:05.960 --> 14:07.090
Where is Lord Jiang?

14:07.420 --> 14:08.600
Fan Xiu came to take her leave,

14:08.600 --> 14:09.870
but why haven't we seen Lord Jiang?

14:09.870 --> 14:11.530
Could he be hiding somewhere?

14:12.430 --> 14:13.170
Lord Jiang

14:13.200 --> 14:14.730
must be reluctant to part with Fan Xiu.

14:14.730 --> 14:15.450
He's probably hiding somewhere,

14:15.450 --> 14:16.570
secretly taking off his mask

14:16.570 --> 14:17.830
and wiping away tears.

14:20.340 --> 14:21.200
Come, have some more.

14:21.200 --> 14:22.080
Lord Jiang is here—
quick, quick,

14:22.080 --> 14:22.810
back to work!

14:23.440 --> 14:24.240
Hurry, hurry!

14:26.060 --> 14:26.870
Lord Jiang.

14:30.150 --> 14:31.810
Take these books back with you

14:31.840 --> 14:33.070
and read them.

14:32.330 --> 14:33.370
[The Customs and Geography of Daduan]

14:35.320 --> 14:36.580
Thank you, Lord Jiang.

14:36.990 --> 14:37.690
Remember,

14:38.100 --> 14:39.500
do not underestimate it.

14:40.010 --> 14:42.670
The selection exam is not
as simple as you think.

14:43.000 --> 14:44.860
If you fail to become an official,

14:45.150 --> 14:46.960
then we shall not meet again.

14:49.150 --> 14:50.340
Rest assured, Lord Jiang.

14:50.340 --> 14:51.150
I, Fan Xiu,

14:51.440 --> 14:53.090
will not let you down.

15:08.550 --> 15:09.550
Your Excellency,

15:09.770 --> 15:11.510
this is the roster you requested.

15:11.510 --> 15:12.150
All the names on it

15:12.150 --> 15:14.410
were personally promoted by Lord Zheng.

15:16.340 --> 15:17.800
Just leave it there for me.

15:29.390 --> 15:30.480
Anything else?

15:32.110 --> 15:33.110
Your Excellency,

15:33.280 --> 15:34.650
today is the day Miss Fan Yun

15:34.650 --> 15:36.250
leaves the Commerce Bureau.

15:36.540 --> 15:37.780
How can you sit here

15:37.800 --> 15:39.000
and not go see her off?

15:39.570 --> 15:40.620
I won't go.

15:41.960 --> 15:43.490
There's a box on this table—

15:43.850 --> 15:45.650
it's a gift prepared for Fan Yun.

15:45.910 --> 15:47.440
You two, help me deliver it.

15:48.130 --> 15:50.660
Your Excellency,
you're not going in person?

15:53.150 --> 15:54.880
Just do as His Excellency says.

15:59.630 --> 16:00.830
What's going on here?

16:01.100 --> 16:01.800
Are you stupid or what?

16:01.800 --> 16:04.080
Judging from what happened
at the morning assembly today,

16:04.080 --> 16:06.540
there will surely
be tougher battles ahead.

16:08.270 --> 16:09.750
What exactly went wrong?

16:11.270 --> 16:14.800
Are you two seriously talking
about me right in front of my face?

16:16.150 --> 16:17.270
If you don't hurry and go see her off,

16:17.270 --> 16:18.870
Fan Yun will already be home.

16:21.270 --> 16:22.330
And one more thing—

16:23.870 --> 16:26.070
what happened at the morning assembly,

16:26.460 --> 16:29.260
not a single word of it is
to be mentioned to Fan Yun.

16:32.400 --> 16:33.660
Yes, Your Excellency.

16:59.360 --> 17:00.610
Young master,
feel free to have a look around.

17:00.610 --> 17:03.810
These are all top-grade items—
truly the best of the best.

17:38.850 --> 17:40.070
In my younger sister's heart,

17:40.070 --> 17:42.370
Your Excellency is like
the blazing sun high in the sky.

17:42.370 --> 17:44.120
She feels unworthy
and ashamed,

17:44.120 --> 17:45.370
believing she does not deserve

17:45.370 --> 17:46.350
to stand before Your Excellency,

17:46.350 --> 17:47.260
and so she

17:47.290 --> 17:48.550
quietly left halfway.

17:48.750 --> 17:50.420
Miss Wei's younger brother.

17:53.230 --> 17:55.290
Are you trying to pick a fight or what?

18:00.200 --> 18:01.000
Little birds

18:01.020 --> 18:02.080
also need freedom.

18:03.400 --> 18:05.160
Great minds think alike.

18:07.440 --> 18:08.400
Wei Rong.

18:08.960 --> 18:09.890
It really is you!

18:11.000 --> 18:12.000
It smells so good.

18:17.480 --> 18:19.300
These are sesame balls.

18:19.680 --> 18:20.810
They're delicious—

18:21.070 --> 18:21.920
try one.

18:26.010 --> 18:26.850
So, how is it?

18:27.000 --> 18:28.060
Does it taste good?

18:28.310 --> 18:30.290
The texture
of the individual sesame seeds,

18:30.290 --> 18:31.770
the soft glutinous cake,

18:31.800 --> 18:33.200
and the red bean filling—

18:33.440 --> 18:35.370
it's truly a perfect combination.

18:43.000 --> 18:44.200
At a moment like this,

18:44.240 --> 18:46.100
you could actually say thank you.

19:11.010 --> 19:13.010
This beautiful melody—

19:13.040 --> 19:14.240
could it be

19:14.260 --> 19:15.860
a return gift for the sesame balls?

19:15.860 --> 19:18.390
You're free to interpret it
however you wish.

19:20.640 --> 19:21.440
Wei Rong.

19:22.870 --> 19:23.690
Lord Wei.

19:24.620 --> 19:26.750
Isn't this my foolish fourth brother?

19:26.790 --> 19:28.040
I haven't even asked you yet—

19:28.040 --> 19:29.410
what are you doing here?

19:30.550 --> 19:32.660
Wandering has no destination anyway.

19:32.660 --> 19:34.160
I just came along to take part
in the selection exam.

19:34.160 --> 19:35.950
You're here to take the selection exam?

19:35.950 --> 19:37.550
Taking the exam isn't important.

19:37.550 --> 19:39.610
What matters is eating sesame balls.

19:42.000 --> 19:42.640
You...

19:43.830 --> 19:44.600
Lord Wei,

19:45.040 --> 19:46.420
is your younger brother

19:46.900 --> 19:48.010
always like this?

19:48.040 --> 19:48.780
He's always been like this.

19:48.780 --> 19:49.640
Don't mind him.

19:49.760 --> 19:50.360
By the way,

19:51.750 --> 19:52.270
His Excellency

19:52.270 --> 19:53.480
knows you're leaving the Commerce Bureau,

19:53.480 --> 19:54.590
but he couldn't get away himself,

19:54.590 --> 19:56.250
so he specially asked me and Yan Jiang

19:56.250 --> 19:58.580
to bring over the gift
he prepared for you.

19:59.880 --> 20:00.640
Yan Jiang?

20:01.400 --> 20:02.730
Where is Lord Yan Jiang?

20:05.400 --> 20:07.260
That guy probably got lost again.

20:14.160 --> 20:17.540
W-What on earth is His Excellency
up to this time?

20:17.910 --> 20:20.170
What an exquisite
and unusual figurine.

20:21.030 --> 20:23.630
Maybe his craftsmanship
just isn't very good.

20:27.920 --> 20:28.950
Either way,

20:29.440 --> 20:32.040
please thank His Excellency
for his kindness.

20:34.930 --> 20:36.380
Where did Wei Rong go?

20:36.410 --> 20:37.170
Yeah,

20:37.190 --> 20:38.790
he was just here a moment ago.

20:39.790 --> 20:40.460
Anyway,

20:40.480 --> 20:41.550
it seems like whenever he wants,

20:41.550 --> 20:43.030
he can slip into anywhere—

20:43.050 --> 20:45.750
and disappear just as easily,
anytime, anywhere.

20:45.750 --> 20:46.430
No,

20:46.510 --> 20:47.640
I have to go find him.

20:49.420 --> 20:51.550
How can there be such a strange person?

20:52.400 --> 20:53.070
Lord Wei,

20:53.070 --> 20:54.380
I'll go with you.

21:07.750 --> 21:10.030
Your younger brother is something else.

21:11.400 --> 21:13.750
Isn't that exactly
why he's called Wei Rong?

21:13.750 --> 21:14.640
The character "Rong" in Wei Rong

21:14.640 --> 21:15.800
comes from our Wei family's
ancestral teaching:

21:15.800 --> 21:17.440
"One who is Rong
is virtuous and accomplished."

21:17.440 --> 21:18.280
It is said

21:18.310 --> 21:20.460
that only those chosen by fate are worthy
of being given those two characters.

21:20.460 --> 21:21.550
I am the fourth son,

21:21.570 --> 21:23.570
with three elder brothers above me,

21:24.130 --> 21:25.330
yet unexpectedly,

21:25.360 --> 21:26.660
the one who was granted the name Wei Rong

21:26.660 --> 21:28.420
is the youngest in our family.

21:30.430 --> 21:31.750
So outstanding

21:32.000 --> 21:34.350
that he can even make four older brothers
seem irrelevant.

21:34.350 --> 21:36.870
Though he is
a rather peculiar younger brother,

21:36.870 --> 21:38.310
for our Wei family,

21:39.350 --> 21:40.880
he is nonetheless our hope.

21:42.070 --> 21:43.590
It's just that he loves
wandering too much—

21:43.590 --> 21:44.750
only ever seen in glimpses, never in full.

21:44.750 --> 21:46.830
Even if you catch him, you can barely
get a few words out of him.

21:46.830 --> 21:47.920
So in other words,

21:47.920 --> 21:49.480
he neither obeys others blindly

21:49.480 --> 21:51.160
nor is easily used by others,

21:51.160 --> 21:51.790
is that correct?

21:51.790 --> 21:53.390
-Lord Yan Jiang.
-Yan Jiang.

21:54.550 --> 21:55.750
When did you get here?

21:56.110 --> 21:56.590
I...

21:56.590 --> 21:57.830
I've been here the whole time.

21:57.830 --> 21:59.690
You're the one who got lost, okay?

21:59.720 --> 22:00.510
Is that so?

22:04.830 --> 22:05.460
Wei Rong,

22:05.910 --> 22:08.410
w-what are you doing now?

22:08.560 --> 22:09.660
I'm sleepy.

22:09.770 --> 22:11.830
I'm just going to sleep here tonight.

22:16.720 --> 22:18.010
Where did you stay last night?

22:18.010 --> 22:19.010
Last night?

22:19.890 --> 22:21.600
I slept while watching the stars.

22:21.600 --> 22:23.600
Sleeping while watching the stars?

22:24.400 --> 22:26.050
That's basically sleeping on the streets.

22:26.050 --> 22:27.720
The sky as my quilt,
the earth as my bed—

22:27.720 --> 22:29.380
what's so strange about that?

22:31.030 --> 22:32.270
No matter what,

22:32.270 --> 22:34.000
you definitely can't sleep here.

22:34.000 --> 22:35.030
Or else,

22:35.030 --> 22:35.740
Wei Rong,

22:35.820 --> 22:37.750
why don't you go back with Lord Wei?

22:38.640 --> 22:41.330
I refuse to stay the night
with such a mundane person.

22:41.330 --> 22:41.930
You...

22:42.400 --> 22:43.600
Then come to my place.

22:43.700 --> 22:44.370
How about that?

22:44.370 --> 22:46.830
Lord Fan, how could you
possibly handle him?

22:50.440 --> 22:51.570
Then how about this—

22:52.200 --> 22:52.800
Yan Jiang,

22:53.550 --> 22:54.310
let him

22:54.850 --> 22:56.240
stay at your residence.

22:57.400 --> 22:58.400
Mine?

23:00.120 --> 23:00.820
Sure.

23:03.970 --> 23:04.630
Sure...

23:08.220 --> 23:09.940
I'd rather have him go to your place.

23:09.940 --> 23:11.180
What?

23:11.200 --> 23:13.330
He chose your place on his own.

23:24.470 --> 23:26.320
It's all just clichés—

23:26.350 --> 23:28.350
this room really has
no charm at all.

23:29.150 --> 23:30.130
I've been here for so long;

23:30.130 --> 23:31.830
where are your family members?

23:31.830 --> 23:32.550
Aren't you going to offer

23:32.550 --> 23:34.020
your guest any good food?

24:58.660 --> 25:00.030
It should be like this.

25:02.130 --> 25:03.530
Lord Yan Jiang,

25:03.550 --> 25:04.590
Wei Rong,

25:04.620 --> 25:07.280
you're here at the market
to buy vegetables too?

25:07.380 --> 25:08.350
Don't even bring it up.

25:08.350 --> 25:10.150
I didn't sleep at all last night—

25:10.510 --> 25:11.790
all because of this guy.

25:11.790 --> 25:14.050
I have no idea
what's going on in his head.

25:14.590 --> 25:15.590
Him?

25:16.070 --> 25:16.920
What did he do?

25:16.920 --> 25:17.480
He...

25:32.140 --> 25:32.900
Pulling...

25:33.560 --> 25:34.760
pulling...

25:35.960 --> 25:37.110
pulling weeds early in the morning.

25:37.110 --> 25:37.720
Right.

25:41.110 --> 25:42.480
That's not bad, actually.

25:42.480 --> 25:43.680
It cleans the courtyard

25:43.680 --> 25:45.010
and trains the body.

25:45.370 --> 25:47.330
You should worry more about him—

25:47.350 --> 25:49.030
he can even get lost inside his own house.

25:49.030 --> 25:50.110
Mind your own business.

25:50.110 --> 25:51.780
All right, all right,

25:51.800 --> 25:53.200
both of you stop arguing.

25:53.900 --> 25:55.540
Well, Wei Rong,

25:55.760 --> 25:56.730
you should consider

25:56.730 --> 25:58.440
other people's feelings
when you do things.

25:58.440 --> 26:00.200
If you cause trouble

26:00.220 --> 26:02.130
or upset others,

26:02.320 --> 26:03.270
that's not good.

26:04.640 --> 26:05.510
Why don't you

26:06.080 --> 26:07.840
apologize

26:07.860 --> 26:08.860
to Lord Yan Jiang?

26:11.500 --> 26:12.940
To apologize,

26:12.960 --> 26:14.000
you should say,

26:14.030 --> 26:14.760
"I'm sorry."

26:16.940 --> 26:19.350
I am sorry.

26:23.100 --> 26:23.790
Then...

26:24.890 --> 26:25.720
never mind.

26:26.240 --> 26:27.970
I'll just go back and take a nap.

26:30.880 --> 26:32.350
But Lord Yan Jiang,

26:33.140 --> 26:34.220
isn't your home

26:34.680 --> 26:36.030
actually that way?

26:38.790 --> 26:39.500
Is it?

26:40.410 --> 26:40.930
Right.

26:41.270 --> 26:42.010
This way.

26:48.240 --> 26:49.880
That being the case,

26:50.400 --> 26:51.240
why don't you

26:51.440 --> 26:53.240
stay at my place today?

26:53.350 --> 26:56.410
That way we can review
for the selection exam together.

26:56.850 --> 26:57.640
Alright.

27:04.400 --> 27:05.060
Wei Rong,

27:05.370 --> 27:06.440
eat more.

27:07.900 --> 27:08.810
Don't stand on ceremony—

27:08.810 --> 27:10.610
just treat it like your own home.

27:10.680 --> 27:11.410
Wei Rong,

27:12.110 --> 27:12.750
here.

27:15.810 --> 27:16.390
Alright.

27:18.470 --> 27:19.670
This is the first time

27:20.120 --> 27:21.880
I've seen you smile.

27:23.850 --> 27:25.980
That's nothing to be surprised about.

27:30.440 --> 27:31.240
True.

27:31.700 --> 27:33.200
A full stomach makes
for a good night's sleep.

27:33.200 --> 27:34.750
I walked way too much during the day.

27:34.750 --> 27:35.920
Then eat more.

27:37.070 --> 27:39.270
Weren't we supposed to study together?

27:40.080 --> 27:40.800
Right,

27:42.270 --> 27:43.900
can we have more buns too?

27:49.150 --> 27:51.520
-Sure, sure.
-Of course, of course.

27:52.920 --> 27:53.810
Wei Rong,

27:53.920 --> 27:54.830
actually...

27:55.240 --> 27:56.670
you look really good
when you smile.

27:56.670 --> 27:58.320
You should smile more often.

28:05.110 --> 28:05.980
What?

28:06.000 --> 28:07.610
Why didn't you say earlier?

28:07.640 --> 28:08.350
Master,

28:08.640 --> 28:10.120
I, Zheng Yi, failed in my task.

28:10.120 --> 28:11.000
Your letter

28:11.040 --> 28:12.760
was intercepted by Lord Lyu.

28:13.200 --> 28:15.460
Well, well, Lyu Wenzhong!

28:15.750 --> 28:17.440
Why have you summoned me?

28:19.730 --> 28:21.060
Quick, quick, quick...

28:24.020 --> 28:25.170
Lord Lyu,

28:26.310 --> 28:28.110
my master has caught a cold again

28:28.140 --> 28:28.710
and is not fit

28:28.710 --> 28:29.830
to receive guests today.

28:29.830 --> 28:31.890
Perhaps you should come another day.

28:33.110 --> 28:33.880
Look at him—

28:35.200 --> 28:37.600
he's right there,
all flushed and healthy.

28:38.010 --> 28:39.660
How does he look ill?

28:39.720 --> 28:41.010
No, Lord Lyu.

28:41.170 --> 28:43.110
Please, you should come another day.

28:43.110 --> 28:44.600
Get on with your work.

28:45.170 --> 28:45.810
Go on,

28:47.280 --> 28:48.680
-out you go.
-Lord Lyu...

29:01.470 --> 29:03.600
This is utterly improper!

29:05.160 --> 29:06.380
Zheng,

29:06.410 --> 29:07.750
still angry?

29:10.200 --> 29:11.080
Fine—

29:11.560 --> 29:12.730
here, I'm returning it to you.

29:12.180 --> 29:13.380
[Letter of Resignation]

29:19.670 --> 29:21.040
Lord Lyu,

29:21.060 --> 29:24.000
do you think that by intercepting
my resignation letter,

29:24.000 --> 29:26.280
no one

29:26.350 --> 29:29.010
will oppose the selection exam
reform anymore?

29:30.060 --> 29:31.960
This only represents me personally.

29:31.960 --> 29:35.200
The Nine Noble Families
are not just for show.

29:37.720 --> 29:38.640
Zheng,

29:39.750 --> 29:41.960
everyone here knows exactly

29:41.960 --> 29:44.290
how powerful your resignation letter is.

29:44.400 --> 29:45.940
Once it's made public,

29:46.790 --> 29:48.420
it will inevitably

29:48.890 --> 29:50.130
cause a split—

29:51.400 --> 29:52.200
both the selection exam faction

29:52.200 --> 29:54.860
and the noble faction
will suffer heavy losses.

29:55.240 --> 29:58.630
Now that Qi Zheng
has used his position as the governor

29:59.590 --> 30:03.450
to guarantee the pilot implementation
of the selection exam reform,

30:03.630 --> 30:06.420
if he sees this resignation letter,

30:06.510 --> 30:07.130
tell me—

30:07.840 --> 30:10.030
how is he supposed to live with that?

30:12.470 --> 30:13.530
That's his choice,

30:14.640 --> 30:16.900
going against the proper duty of a ruler.

30:18.600 --> 30:19.160
This

30:19.810 --> 30:21.160
only represents me.

30:21.790 --> 30:23.050
Can't I just hide away?

30:23.190 --> 30:25.050
Can't I just turn a blind eye to it?

30:28.330 --> 30:30.090
Someone! Come here!

30:34.360 --> 30:36.720
My three-color glazed vase!

30:36.750 --> 30:38.070
Zheng, don't get worked up—
don't get worked up.

30:38.070 --> 30:39.750
Let me take a look...

30:42.200 --> 30:44.120
Isn't this

30:44.310 --> 30:46.350
the one I gave you

30:46.720 --> 30:48.480
for your 50th birthday?

30:50.000 --> 30:50.770
Fine then—

30:50.820 --> 30:52.870
consider it taken back.

30:56.120 --> 30:56.750
Zheng!

30:57.510 --> 30:58.330
Zheng...

31:00.570 --> 31:01.370
My...

31:05.950 --> 31:07.080
This jade pendant—

31:07.160 --> 31:09.350
I gave it to you back then.

31:09.350 --> 31:11.810
Might as well say
you don't want this either.

31:12.920 --> 31:13.640
You...

31:14.440 --> 31:16.550
How can you be so childish?

31:17.170 --> 31:19.370
This is my residence.

31:19.410 --> 31:21.470
What can you do to me?

31:29.440 --> 31:31.440
This old authentic painting—

31:31.440 --> 31:34.160
I had people search all Nine Cities

31:34.160 --> 31:35.400
just to find it for you, didn't I?

31:35.400 --> 31:36.200
That's right.

31:36.610 --> 31:37.830
Fine—you might as well

31:37.830 --> 31:39.070
not keep it.

31:40.270 --> 31:41.070
How dare you?

31:41.750 --> 31:43.070
Just see if I dare!

31:43.070 --> 31:44.260
Please, hold back—

31:44.280 --> 31:45.620
don't do anything rash.

31:46.000 --> 31:48.160
Don't do anything rash.

31:48.180 --> 31:49.630
Zheng,

31:50.110 --> 31:52.510
you know very well
you can't act on impulse.

31:52.790 --> 31:54.190
Once this letter is sent,

31:54.480 --> 31:56.800
it's truly irreversible.

32:05.360 --> 32:05.920
This...

32:08.180 --> 32:09.220
I...

32:10.240 --> 32:11.070
You...

32:12.270 --> 32:12.840
You...

32:14.080 --> 32:14.930
Get out!

32:16.400 --> 32:17.240
Go, go, go.

32:34.410 --> 32:35.380
Zheng,

32:36.000 --> 32:37.770
the Nine Cities are like this painting—

32:37.770 --> 32:39.400
once it's ruined, it's ruined.

32:39.400 --> 32:40.660
There's no going back.

32:44.370 --> 32:45.770
Zheng, if you truly force

32:46.110 --> 32:47.800
Qi Zheng

32:48.420 --> 32:50.550
to abdicate his position as governor,

32:51.260 --> 32:52.150
by then

32:52.170 --> 32:54.760
the Nine Cities will be left leaderless.

32:56.240 --> 32:58.680
Before the Nine Noble Families
even grow disheartened,

32:58.680 --> 33:01.280
the realm will already
have fallen into chaos.

33:07.460 --> 33:08.380
Zheng,

33:09.240 --> 33:10.570
do you really want to see

33:10.790 --> 33:12.200
the succession struggle

33:12.880 --> 33:13.930
from

33:14.310 --> 33:15.370
thirteen years ago

33:16.310 --> 33:17.270
repeated,

33:17.640 --> 33:19.110
with rivers of blood,

33:20.940 --> 33:24.070
before you'll stop?

33:27.820 --> 33:28.780
Zheng,

33:30.220 --> 33:31.420
and after that?

33:32.240 --> 33:34.300
Who will inherit the governor's seat

33:34.510 --> 33:36.370
and reclaim control of the realm?

34:07.480 --> 34:08.400
Fan Yun,

34:09.350 --> 34:10.489
I woke up hungry.

34:10.840 --> 34:12.770
Do you have any late-night snacks?

34:13.760 --> 34:14.710
Yes.

34:17.030 --> 34:17.920
Wei Rong,

34:18.510 --> 34:20.989
all you ever do is eat and sleep.

34:21.010 --> 34:22.560
And when you're finally awake,

34:22.560 --> 34:24.159
you only ever play the flute.

34:25.230 --> 34:27.980
If someone like you can actually
pass the selection exam,

34:27.980 --> 34:29.940
then I might as well give up hope.

34:29.989 --> 34:31.650
If you fail the selection exam

34:31.760 --> 34:33.380
and end up unmarried,

34:33.810 --> 34:35.670
I'll hire you as my personal chef.

34:38.940 --> 34:39.790
Alright,

34:39.820 --> 34:41.620
I'll go get you something to eat.

34:48.150 --> 34:49.150
Wei Rong,

34:49.380 --> 34:51.980
are you really not going
to stay a few more days?

34:53.250 --> 34:55.179
I've already troubled you enough.

34:56.110 --> 34:56.909
Alright then.

34:57.100 --> 34:58.570
Take good care of yourself.

34:58.570 --> 34:59.300
Alright.

35:04.360 --> 35:05.140
Lord Fan Qi,

35:06.270 --> 35:08.000
I, Wei Rong, have caused you trouble.

35:08.000 --> 35:08.760
Not at all.

35:11.070 --> 35:12.200
Just remember this—

35:12.730 --> 35:13.870
you are my soulmate.

35:14.350 --> 35:15.550
A soulmate?

35:15.770 --> 35:17.210
A future soulmate.

35:18.510 --> 35:19.140
Alright.

35:19.590 --> 35:21.070
A future soulmate.

35:24.530 --> 35:25.390
Then

35:26.840 --> 35:27.970
we shall meet again.

35:42.760 --> 35:43.550
He's someone

35:43.550 --> 35:45.700
who loves a free and unrestrained life.

35:45.700 --> 35:46.850
Why does he

35:47.300 --> 35:48.700
insist on taking the selection exam?

35:48.700 --> 35:50.620
Not only is he taking the selection exam—

35:50.620 --> 35:51.680
he's even promised

35:52.070 --> 35:53.360
to make it into the top three.

35:53.360 --> 35:54.450
Top three?

35:54.800 --> 35:55.470
Why?

35:56.020 --> 35:57.060
Because that was

35:57.440 --> 36:00.650
the condition the Wei family set
for granting him his freedom.

36:00.650 --> 36:01.850
I see...

36:07.960 --> 36:09.130
He really is

36:09.160 --> 36:11.320
suited to that kind of free lifestyle.

36:12.410 --> 36:13.010
By the way,

36:13.950 --> 36:15.050
I should also thank you, Fan Yun.

36:15.050 --> 36:16.050
Thank me?

36:16.630 --> 36:18.060
You're the only one

36:18.190 --> 36:20.250
who didn't avoid my younger brother.

36:20.460 --> 36:21.560
Avoid him?

36:21.930 --> 36:23.180
Why would I avoid him?

36:24.160 --> 36:25.760
Wei Rong has always

36:25.920 --> 36:27.290
been very lonely

36:27.960 --> 36:29.560
because of his personality.

36:31.000 --> 36:33.030
That's because he's a genius.

36:34.410 --> 36:35.480
He can see things

36:35.510 --> 36:37.010
others cannot.

36:37.890 --> 36:39.280
But conversely,

36:39.880 --> 36:42.670
what ordinary people can see,

36:43.370 --> 36:44.810
he cannot.

36:46.360 --> 36:47.590
That must be

36:47.590 --> 36:48.700
such a lonely,

36:48.910 --> 36:51.060
isolating feeling.

36:55.400 --> 36:56.230
Fortunately,

36:56.590 --> 36:57.840
he has a friend now.

37:04.000 --> 37:05.560
A soulmate...

37:09.150 --> 37:12.440
Past mistakes—
what should be punished?

37:12.800 --> 37:16.640
Future concerns—
what should be guarded against?

37:18.060 --> 37:20.500
What should be guarded against...

37:44.550 --> 37:45.760
Young Master Qiyan,

37:47.150 --> 37:48.460
what brings you here?

37:48.490 --> 37:49.220
Are you free?

37:50.280 --> 37:51.280
I...

37:51.680 --> 37:52.810
Young Master Qiyan,

37:53.000 --> 37:54.600
is there something urgent?

37:55.180 --> 37:56.700
Not really.

37:56.820 --> 37:58.300
I just came to see you.

38:01.900 --> 38:02.750
Then...

38:03.770 --> 38:05.580
Then maybe come
another day instead.

38:05.580 --> 38:07.610
I still need to review my lessons.

38:32.020 --> 38:33.830
I really do need to study.

38:34.370 --> 38:35.120
So...

38:36.120 --> 38:36.980
I should leave?

38:45.380 --> 38:46.440
What,

38:46.630 --> 38:48.690
am I the one who should leave instead?

38:59.570 --> 39:00.420
War

39:01.150 --> 39:02.780
is a matter of vital
importance to the state—

39:02.780 --> 39:04.340
a place of life and death,

39:05.240 --> 39:06.700
a path to survival or ruin.

39:06.780 --> 39:08.490
It must not be neglected.

39:09.720 --> 39:11.700
To subdue the enemy
without fighting

39:11.700 --> 39:13.230
is the highest excellence.

39:13.810 --> 39:15.140
If that is not possible,

39:15.590 --> 39:17.480
one must resort to a secondary approach:

39:17.480 --> 39:18.790
evaluate it through five factors

